headline: Beechcraft M-346N Unveiled as Ready-Now Solution for U.S. Navy Undergraduate Jet Training System
summary: WICHITA, Kan., July 28, 2025--Textron Aviation Defense LLC is offering the Beechcraft M-346N jet as a "ready-now" solution the U.S. Navy UJTS program.

headline: Hexcel Q2 Earnings Beat Estimates, Sales Decline Y/Y
summary: Hexcel's Q2 revenues outpace forecasts, but shrinking margins and lower commercial aerospace sales volume weigh on results.

headline: Kautex Textron Wins Significant BEV Battery Housing Contract with Leading Automotive OEM
summary: BONN, Germany, July 28, 2025--Kautex has announced an order from a leading automotive OEM for a full-BEV thermoplastic composite lower battery housing unit.
